title: The Babys - Head First (Out Of Print) (320 Kbps MP3) {solstars}
description:
Released in 1978, this was their best charting album. The title cut and 'Everytime I Think of You' were radio favorites. My PERSONAL favorite is "I Was One", which always stood out to me.  This is the re-mastered 2001 release.  This album is now out of print and VERY hard to find.  I hope you like it.


1. Love Don't Prove I'm Right
2. Everytime I Think of You
3. I Was One
4. White Lightning
5. Run to Mexico
6. Head First
7. You (Got It)
8. Please Don't Leave Me Here
9. California


All of my rips are taken from the original CD.  Enjoy!
